 ### 11) `POST /logout`
 Clears auth and CSRF cookies.
+Requires access JWT cookie plus `X-CSRF-TOKEN` matching `csrf_access_token`.
+
+## CSRF Errors
+
+State-changing auth endpoints reject missing or mismatched CSRF header/cookie pairs with:
+
+```json
+{
+  "detail": "Invalid or missing CSRF token"
+}
+```
+
+The status code is `401`. JWT validation still runs after CSRF validation on authenticated endpoints,
+so invalid, expired, or wrong-type JWT cookies continue to return `"Invalid or expired token"`.
 
